==Making a key==
===Talking to Thurgo===
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Can you make me another of Sir Vyvin's swords?}}
* {{topt|quest=No|What is that cape you're wearing?}}
* {{topt|I need some help with a 'special key'.}}
** '''Player:''' I need some help with a 'special key'.
** '''Thurgo:''' A key? What for?
** '''Player:''' Well, truth be told, I'm not sure it's really a key that I need. I just need something that can open a crate.
** '''Thurgo:''' Ah, well a crowbar should do that. It's a simple tool.
** '''Player:''' Can you help me make one?
** '''Thurgo:''' I can indeed. We'll need a hammer, a steel bar, and of course, a redberry pie.
** {{tcond|If the player does not have all of the materials:}}
*** '''Player:''' I don't have all of that I'm afraid...
*** '''Thurgo:''' Well, come back when you do.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{tselect|Make a crowbar with Thurgo?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** {{tbox|pic=Crowbar detail.png|You hammer a crowbar out of your steel bar, while Thurgo directs you with a pie-filled mouth.}}
*** {{tact|receives=a [[crowbar]]}}
*** '''Thurgo:''' That should do nicely.
*** '''Player:''' Thanks! I should probably see what Steve makes of this.
*** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** {{tact|end}}

