===Talking to Steve Beanie with the 'special key'===
* ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Yarr! What will it be?
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Let's see what you have.}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Any word from Old Grog?}}
* {{topt|I made that 'special key' you needed.}}
** '''Player:''' I made that 'special key' you needed.
** {{tbox|pic=Crowbar detail.png|You show Steve the crowbar.}}
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Aha! There she crows! This is perfect!
** '''Player:''' I'm glad you approve. Shall I use it to crack this crate open?
** {{tbox|pic=Crowbar detail.png|You raise the crowbar hopefully.}}
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Wait!
** {{tbox|pic=Crowbar detail.png|You lower the crowbar dejectedly.}}
** '''Player:''' What's wrong?
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' An artifact{{sic|British spelling is 'artefact'.}} of this power needs a test before we try it on our precious looty!
** '''Player:''' ...
** '''Player:''' Fine. What should I test it on?
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' I noticed a crate of grog floating around by the north westmost{{sic}} island of the Pandemonium. Cast off your keel and sail your vessel over there.
** '''Player:''' And then?
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Well, you open it with your new key and sample the contents, of course.
** '''Player:''' Why would I even want to do that? How do you even know it's drinkable?
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' I'm a true pirate, so I know good grog when I see it. As for why, no sailor has truly experienced the sea until they have drunk everything it has to offer.
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' In fact, you should keep a log of it all. I know I do!
** '''Player:''' Okay... this doesn't seem very healthy, but fine.
** ''''Squawking' Steve Beanie:''' Yarr! That's the spirit!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Could you tell me about the Pandemonium's one rule?}}
* {{topt|quest=No|Nothing, thanks.}}

